# Next.js Integration Guide (`boundless` project)

Based on your project structure, here is the exact way to integrate the map.

## 1. Install Dependencies
Run this in your terminal:
```bash
npm install leaflet
# Optional: TypeScript types if you want strict checking
npm install -D @types/leaflet
```

## 2. Add the Component
